window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In Tim LaHaye—creator and co-author of the world-renowned Left Behind series—and Craig Parshall’s <i>Edge of Apocalypse</i> unabridged audio download, Joshua Jordan’s new weapons defense system will secure America against an array of new enemies, including a nuclear strike on New York City by North Korea. But global forces are mounting and corrupt government leaders will go to any extreme to prevent an impending economic catastrophe. As world events begin setting the stage for the “end of days” foretold in Revelation, Jordan must weigh the personal price he must pay to save the nation he loves.</p>"; 
